[31m-## How It Works[m
[31m-[m
[31m-The CMO Agent works by:[m
[32m+[m[32m## Cleanup[m
 [m
[31m-1. Loading memory files from the `shared/memory` directory using LangChain's document loaders[m
[31m-2. Embedding these documents using OpenAI's embeddings[m
[31m-3. Creating a vector store for semantic search[m
[31m-4. When a query is made, it retrieves relevant context from the vector store[m
[31m-5. The context is passed to the OpenAI model, which generates a response[m
[31m-6. (Optional) The response is sent as a Discord direct message notification[m
[31m-[m
[31m-## Interacting with the CMO Agent[m
[31m-[m
[31m-Currently, the CMO Agent generates a weekly marketing strategy based on the knowledge stored in the memory files. The strategy includes:[m
[31m-[m
[31m-- Main goal of the week[m
[31m-- Campaign ideas[m
[31m-- Target audiences[m
[31m-- Recommended channels[m
[31m-- Metrics to track[m
[31m-[m
[31m-If Discord integration is configured, the agent will also send the weekly strategy as a direct message to the specified Discord user.[m
[31m-[m
